# Suppressed CVEs — reviewed and accepted pending upstream fixes
# These are OS-level vulnerabilities in the Alpine base image with fix versions
# that have not yet shipped. They will be resolved automatically when the base
# image is updated. Remove entries here once the base image contains the fix.

# openssl: NULL pointer dereference in CMS — fix in openssl 3.5.6-r0 (not yet in Alpine)
# Affects: libcrypto3, libssl3 in node:22-alpine and nginx:1.29-alpine
CVE-2026-28390

# zlib: buffer overflow in untgz utility — fix in zlib 1.3.2-r0 (not yet in Alpine)
# Affects: zlib in node:22-alpine and nginx:1.29-alpine
CVE-2026-22184
